### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/src/api/users.php

### Get single user by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/src/api/users.php?id=3

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:8080/src/api/users.php
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "user"
}

### Update user
PUT http://localhost:8080/src/api/users.php
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 4,
  "name": "John Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "role": "staff"
}

### Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:8080/src/api/users.php?id=4
